{"tid":1257835,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS5] SomaSim聯合創始人表示 PS5 採用新技術，光線反射將隨處可見","createTime":"2019-06-25T19:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T01:48:23.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3e6120a281a510f7c8a6516d965f9614ea539c","tid":1257835,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T19:06:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2366478236956017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2366478236956017&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDjUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=b6d324ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2366478236956017</a><br />\n<br />\n之前索尼介紹了 #PS5主機 許多細節，它性能強悍讓人印象深刻。 #PS5有更強大的CPU和GPU，並支持光線追踪技術(Ray tracing)。許多玩家擔心支持光追只是個噱頭，有人卻表示在未來，#PS5遊戲搞光線追踪是家常便飯。<br />\n<br />\nSomaSim聯合創始人Matthew Viglione表示PS5 Zen 2處理器將會實現這一目標。 Viglione說：&ldquo;下代遊戲機採用新技術，光線反射將隨處可見。而光線追踪也會像&lsquo;鏡頭光暈&rsquo;那樣普及起來，在遊戲中很常見。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n早先我們介紹過PS主機的硬件性能將貼近電腦，遊戲優化工作將會減輕，移植光追遊戲也會更加方便。<br />\n<br />\nViglione還談到跨平台遊玩：&ldquo;不少平台都在推動跨平台遊玩，最後它也會像遊戲界所有事情一樣由玩家來決定。不管跨不跨平台，平台商都是要向玩家們售賣服務的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nPS5主機上線日期尚未公佈，不過考慮到下代Xbox將於明年年底到來，PS5應該也會於明年推出。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dn87S4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdn87S4e.jpg&h=9e5b7e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Gu3rpf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Gu3rpf.jpg&h=276c832a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hTcP6pg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhTcP6pg.png&h=36868bea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><ins>SIE總裁Jim Ryan發表更多關於PS5的信息︰SSD將成為標配、支持4K分辨率下的120Hz</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1187165 \" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1187165 </a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>《華爾街日報》記者Takashi Mochizuki：索尼將不會在未來12個月內發售下一代PlayStation主機。</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1126328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1126328</a>"},{"pid":"326d341f208c57b1998c10ab8c367dbba67615de","tid":1257835,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff1902618843ae36daf8794a5f30d8a09620e92","tid":1257835,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237a70855f55cdcfda004751006f81c046190fb7","tid":1257835,"uid":18082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"1080p開ray tracing應該得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbbcd8a648ad6a95d0db398a5884f78c0d46d40","tid":1257835,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b689dcefee6104c9d5a096dbcf5a8d1ee7ca6c7","tid":1257835,"uid":135211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"4k120hz 係咪老吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d52ebc013a870e131dd8b433bb0c598b12ce11","tid":1257835,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b689dcefee6104c9d5a096dbcf5a8d1ee7ca6c7","tid":1257835,"uid":135211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"4k120hz 係咪老吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"120hz唔等於120fps <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1fff71227cfdd01621b037f68e38a83a0ad074","tid":1257835,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:48:23.000Z","msg":"部ps4仲可以玩多兩年<im